description:
This is a 27 minute workout called '20 MIN LOWER BODY STRETCH for Recovery and Flexibility (Hamstrings, Butt, & Hips)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Do this 20 minute lower body stretch #WithMe ! This is a quick routine that is focused mainly on the hips and hamstrings. Perfect for recovery/sore muscles and working on your flexibility!
